name: Alt Markets
additional_notices: The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: Alt Markets is a protocol that enables anyone to launch & trade synthetic markets. Markets can represent anything that fits into 1-32 characters. Users can long/short a market by transferring ETH or BNB on Ethereum, Arbitrum, and BSC.
